### FAB - Forest and Biodiversity

This long term experiment tests the consequences of tree biodiversity for forest growth, benefits to animals, protection from disease and pests, and soil fertility.  

*  Cedar Creek [webpage](https://www.cedarcreek.umn.edu/research/experiments/e271) of FAB 1.
